task.summary: Fixed issue where child components were mounted, unmount then re-mounted if they specified a URL. Removed unnecessary rendering of div.
Add ability to call back with the popped out window.
Added ability to specify {childen} as a function so that you can get access to the window object of the popout.
upgraded to prop-types. Made title updatable via props.
Call unmountComponentAtNode so that componentWillUnmount will be called when the popout closes.
Allow specifying a name for the window as using title causes issues when you have multiple windows with the same titles that also update their titles.
Updated dependencies and fixed webpack issues.
Added dummy test to get build to pass.
Fixed issue with loading popouts when about:blank is used (no url). Demos all working now.
Fixed issue with loading popouts when about:blank is used (no url). Demos all working now.
